# Force www and HTTPS version (canonical domain) - CRITICAL for SEO
# These MUST come before any other redirects
https://justice-bot.com/* https://www.justice-bot.com/:splat 301!
http://justice-bot.com/* https://www.justice-bot.com/:splat 301!
http://www.justice-bot.com/* https://www.justice-bot.com/:splat 301!

# Remove trailing slashes (prevents duplicate content)
/*/ /:splat 301!

